description: Emotions were running high for Rebeca Andrade, Simone Biles and Jordan Chiles — but mostly for different reasons — after they prevailed in the final gymnastics event at the Paris Olympics.
title: 3 Black women create an Olympic first in gymnastics

description: There's still a week's worth of medals to be handed out, as competitions ramp up in track and field, soccer and boxing. The excitement has yet to begin in breaking, Taekwondo and weightlifting.
title: What to look forward to in the final leg of the Paris Olympics

description: Biles won silver in the floor exercise final, her fourth of the Paris Olympics. She missed out on the podium in the balance beam after slipping from the beam in her only major mistake of the Games.
title: The gymnast Simone Biles wins silver to close what might be her final Olympic Games

description: The LA indie pop band performs songs off 2023's GIMMICKS.
title: Tune in to a mini-concert with James Supercave

description: After last week’s barn-burner (and serf-burner) of an episode, this season climax qualifies as anti-. The season ends not with a bang, but with a lot of whimpering.
title: 'House of the Dragon' Season 2 finale: Before dragons dance, they gotta stretch

description: All triathletes have been barred from practice swim in Paris river Sunday after poor water quality test results.
title: Belgian Olympic team bows out of triathlon as teammate falls ill after swim in the Seine
